special_powers.description: POWER: Heal Annihilus equal to to his number of Negative Energy tokens.

special_powers.name: ...CAN'T...STOP...LIVING...
special_powers.description: Invincible. When this click is first revealed, give Annihilus a Negative Energy token.

special_powers.name: ANTI-PARTICLES
special_powers.description: Outwit. // When Annihilus is attacked, any positive modifiers of the attacker's attack value become negative. When Annihilus attacks a single character, any positive modifiers of the target's defense value become negative.

special_powers.name: THE POWERS OF THE FANTASTIC FOUR
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose two. Super Skrull has the listed effects until your next turn.  INVISIBLE WOMAN: Sidestep, Stealth, Barrier as FREE but only to generate one marker.  THE THING: Charge, Impervious, Close Combat Expert.  MR. FANTASTIC: Plasticity, Super Senses, Giant Reach: 4.  HUMAN TORCH: Running Shot, Energy Explosion, range of 6.

special_powers.name: THE FORCEFUL RULER OF BALUUR
special_powers.description: Force Blast, Super Strength.

special_powers.name: CONCUSSIVE BLAST
special_powers.description: Energy Explosion.  When he uses it, the character(s) Blastaar originally targeted are dealt penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: CONCUSSIVE BLAST FIGHT
special_powers.description: Charge, Running Shot. FREE: Make a close attack.

special_powers.name: THE LIVING BOMB BURST
special_powers.description: Energy Explosion.  When he uses it, the character(s) Blastaar originally targeted are dealt penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: CONTINUITY
special_powers.description: When Doom 2099, Revolutionary is KO'd, an opponent chooses a number of standard powers equal to your friendly characters on the map. Characters on your force can't use those powers until the end of your next turn.

special_powers.name: DEPOSING TYGER WYLDE
special_powers.description: FREE: Make an attack that deals 1 penetrating damage instead of normal damage. If the attack hits, gain 1 plot point. If the attack hit the highest point (or tied) opposing character on the map, instead gain 3 plot points.

special_powers.name: STEALING THE SHIPMENT AS PART OF THE ZEFIRO RESISTANCE
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose an adjacent opposing character. If they aren't equipped, they modify defense -2 this turn. Otherwise, unequip that character's equipment.

special_powers.name: ONE NATION UNDER DOOM
special_powers.description: FREE: For the rest of the game, for each opposing character, the first time each turn that opposing character would be given a CLOSE, RANGE, MOVE, or POWER action, you may roll a d6. 3-6: That character can't be given that type of action that turn.

special_powers.name: HMMM... AND DO YOU HAVE AN INFINITY GAUNTLET NOW?
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose an opposing character within range and line of fire. That character can't use the EFFECT of Equipment until your next turn.

special_powers.name: GOD OF BATTLEWORLD
special_powers.description: When establishing themed teams, God Emperor Doom gains all Battleworld keywords. // Leadership, Perplex, Colossal Stamina. When God Emperor Doom uses Perplex to target another character with a Battleworld keyword, you may instead modify a combat value except damage by +2 or -2.

special_powers.name: THE WRATH OF DOOM CANNOT BE IGNORED
special_powers.description: CLOSE: Make a close attack. Other characters can't use powers (during that attack).

special_powers.name: YOU HAD TO MEDDLE, DIDN'T YOU?
special_powers.description: STOP. Battle Fury, Exploit Weakness. When this click is first revealed, remove all action tokens from God Emperor Doom.

special_powers.name: FORM THE NEW FANTASTIC FOUR
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, you may replace up to 4 friendly characters with the same number of characters from your Sideline on their starting clicks. All replacement and replaced characters must have the Fantastic Four keyword and different names. The total points of the replacement characters can't exceed the total points of the replaced characters.

special_powers.name: MERCY AT THE LEFT HAND OF DOOM
special_powers.description: Barrier. Barrier as FREE, but only to generate 2 markers. // Sue Storm may use her displayed attack and damage powers as if she occupied a square of her Barrier markers.

special_powers.name: QUEEN OF BATTLEWORLD
special_powers.description: Leadership, Perplex. When Sue Storm uses Perplex to target another character with a Battleworld keyword, you may instead modify a combat value except damage by +2 or -2.

special_powers.name: HUNTING ANOMALIES FROM OTHER WORLDS
special_powers.description: FREE: Roll a d6 and place Valeria Von Doom up to that many squares away. // During your opponent's turn, when an opposing character is placed within 4 squares and line of fire, after resolutions deal them 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: FINDING OUT THE TRUTH ABOUT FATHER
special_powers.description: When a friendly character KO's an opposing character of lower points than them, give Valeria Von Doom an action token that does not deal pushing damage.

special_powers.name: HEAD OF THE INSTITUTE FOR GIFTED YOUTHS
special_powers.description: Leadership, Perplex. When Valeria Von Doom uses Leadership and succeeds, choose a friendly character within 4 squares and line of fire. That character can use Outwit until your next turn.

special_powers.name: MY THOUGHTS AND DESIRES COME TO FRUITION
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose one: If 5 of less of Franklin Von Doom's generated terrain markers are on the map, generate a terrain marker (hindering, water or blocking) in an adjacent square -or- Remove all terrain markers except Debris from a square within range and line of fire.

special_powers.name: MOLECULAR MANIPULATION
special_powers.description: Incapacitate, Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: WANT TO SAVE YOURSELF SOME TIME AND GIVE UP?
special_powers.description: STOP. (Power Cosmic Team Ability), (Colossal Symbol), Impervious.

special_powers.name: REALITY WARP
special_powers.description: Probability Control. Outwit, but only when Franklin Von Doom occupies a terrain marker.

special_powers.name: ULTIMATE ELASTIC BODY
special_powers.description: Plasticity, Super Senses, Giant Reach: 4. // When Maker attacks, characters he targets modify defense -1 for each team ability they can use.

special_powers.name: I'VE BEEN MAKING SOME NEW TOOLS
special_powers.description: Outwit, Perplex. // When Maker hits, after resolutions generate a token that is copy of an Equipment-Object that's equipped to a hit opposing character.  That object has [MAX 1] (for each object name) and isn't scored.

special_powers.name: SPLITTING MYSELF APART
special_powers.description: Shape Change. // POWER: Generate a Maker Two bystander [MAX 1].

special_powers.name: IMPERFECT CLONE
special_powers.description: Maker may use his Outwit, Perplex, and Probability Control as if he occupied this square.

special_powers.name: CONTINUITY
special_powers.description: When Reed Richards, Fixer of Universes is KO'd, Generate a Molecule Man bystander in an opponent's starting area that's friendly to that force.

special_powers.name: NO MORE SUPERHEROICS FOR A WHILE, JUST SCIENCE
special_powers.description: FREE: Outwit, Perplex until your next turn.  At the end of your turn, heal Reed Richards, Fixer Of Universes 1 click if he targeted 1+ opposing characters with Outwit or Perplex this turn.

special_powers.name: UNCOVERING THE REAL SOURCE OF DOOM'S POWER
special_powers.description: FREE: If Reed Richards, Fixer Of Universes occupies an opponent's starting area, generate a Molecule Man bystander [MAX 1].

special_powers.name: CONVINCING OWEN TO UNWRITE VICTOR'S TWISTED REALITY
special_powers.description: FREE: If Reed Richards, Fixer Of Universes is adjacent to Molecule Man, roll a d6.  Deal that much unavoidable damage to the lowest point character on an opponent's force (you choose if there's a tie).

special_powers.name: DID YOU BRING ANY FOOD?
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, if Molecule Man is outside a starting area, KO him.

special_powers.name: UNDERGROUND EMPIRE!
special_powers.description: Stealth, Phasing/Teleport. When Mole Man uses Phasing/Teleport, generate a hindering terrain marker in the square he began and ended his movement in.

special_powers.name: CRAWL OF THE MONSTER ARMY
special_powers.description: Other friendly characters with the Monster keyword have [Improved Movement: Hindering] and "FREE: Move 1 square".

special_powers.name: FIGMENTS OF A MAD NIGHTMARE
special_powers.description: Incapacitate. Incapacitate as FREE, but only to target a character adjacent to 2+ characters.

special_powers.name: AUNT PETUNIA'S HOUSE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose a friendly character. That character's minimum range value when using Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control is 8. If that character's name includes "Franklin" or "Valeria", the 8 becomes 10. CONSOLATION: Opposing character's maximum range value when using Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control is 6.

special_powers.name: LATVERIAN VILLAGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose a friendly character. This game, that character has: 'Mastermind, but only to choose a friendly Latverian Peasant bystander.' // At the beginning of the game, generate 3 Latverian Peasant bystanders in different orange squares. If the chosen character is named Dr. Doom, generate 6 instead. CONSOLATION: At the beginning of the game, generate a Latverian Peasant bystander in your starting area.
